{
  "stem": "23155.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they usually had 1,000 people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had to gather in a big hall.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a fairground, you know, like the, the fairs would be taking place in that building.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Today, it's not there anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There's a big hotel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But at that time, we all gathered.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some people had beds.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I was 992, so there were no beds for, for people after probably 900 or so.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we were lying on the floor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we stayed there, I think, a day and a half or something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I know for sure one night then, because they had to do all the registration and everything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My brother and my mother went before me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They went in August.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You see, it went by addresses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It didn't mean that if you were one family that they put you all together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "If you lived in one place and your mother lived in another place and your brother, it always went by the address.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they lived somewhere else, and I lived somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So they went in August, and I went in September.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They put us on a train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I don't know how many bags it had, or how many cars, rather, it had.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they put us in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we went from Prague to [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Boleslawiec. ?] At that time, the train did not go directly into Terezin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It only went till [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Boleslawiec. ?] And there, they, they threw us out from the train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we had to take whatever we had and march till Terezin.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was quite a, a march.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Everybody had one suitcase or one huge bag.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And you know, we, we took whatever we thought would be good for us.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
